Watermelonz
[[Image:Whitehousewatermelon.jpg|thumb|260px|right|[[Black Jesus|Presidential nigger]] needs his WATERMELONZ]]

Watermelon, also known as Niggermelon, is a fruit which along with [[chikins]], is beloved by [[niggers]].

==Use==
Watermelonz can be used [[Over 9000|100%]] effectively to lure hordes of [[criminals|niggers]]. Upon sighting a watermelon, niggers are powerless to resist the urge to attain and consume it, regardless of [[Rape|whatever they were doing previously]].

